    <item>
      <title>Welcome to My Blog</title>
      <link>https://arindavoodian.github.io</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">example-post-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <p>This is where I share my thoughts, observations, and captured moments. Each post might include photos from my travels, daily life, or just things that caught my eye.</p>
        <p>The design is intentionally minimal—just enough structure to let the content breathe, but nothing that gets in the way of the experience.</p>
        <p><img src="https://arindavoodian.github.io/photos/Street/ARIN0743.jpg" alt="Street photography" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;" /></p>
      ]]></description>
